{
  "stem": "13395.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And now that since we knew that our father is safe, so we thought that we'll stay there and-- and we will be reunited one day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My mother desperately tried to get a visa to go to the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "She even wrote to the embassy in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But there was no way that the Soviets would let anyone in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But this is-- she always took these initiatives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was no stopping her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And she even went to Berlin-- took off her arm band, and nobody would know that she's Jewish, with the fluent German-- and went to the embassy herself.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Well, they took all the information, but we never heard from them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So this failed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We couldn't go and be reunited.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And somehow, we didn't have the courage to go on our own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Just-- I guess she didn't want to endanger us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She would have gone, but she couldn't leave us behind, my sister and I.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it's about 80 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because I remember Jaworzno-- passing by there when we went with my father to Krakow-- was a 90-kilometer bicycle ride before the war.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember stopping at the coal mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had our lunch outside, because there was such nice grass.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's what is so ironical, that in that town we had our lunch on the way-- on our beautiful trip, with beautiful memories.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And now we were brought here into the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we stayed there and were hoping that we'll be there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But unfortunately, things got very bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, you could not get a ration, like food, unless you worked.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we would work for the farmers doing-- you know, in-- in the fields.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we would get some potatoes, so we would work for food.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
